{"iti43:0.1":"Itivuttaka 43 ","iti43:0.2":"Dukanipata ","iti43:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","iti43:0.4":"Ajatasutta ","iti43:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti43:2.1":"“Atthi, bhikkhave, ajatam abhutam akatam asankhatam. ","iti43:2.2":"No cetam, bhikkhave, abhavissa ajatam abhutam akatam asankhatam, nayidha jatassa bhutassa katassa sankhatassa nissaranam pannayetha. ","iti43:2.3":"Yasma ca kho, bhikkhave, atthi ajatam abhutam akatam asankhatam, tasma jatassa bhutassa katassa sankhatassa nissaranam pannayati”ti. ","iti43:2.4":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti43:2.5":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti43:3.1":"“Jatam bhutam samuppannam, ","iti43:3.2":"katam sankhatamaddhuvam; ","iti43:3.3":"Jaramaranasanghatam, ","iti43:3.4":"roganilam pabhanguram. ","iti43:4.1":"Aharanettippabhavam, ","iti43:4.2":"nalam tadabhinanditum; ","iti43:4.3":"Tassa nissaranam santam, ","iti43:4.4":"atakkavacaram dhuvam. ","iti43:5.1":"Ajatam asamuppannam, ","iti43:5.2":"asokam virajam padam; ","iti43:5.3":"Nirodho dukkhadhammanam, ","iti43:5.4":"sankharupasamo sukho”ti. ","iti43:6.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti43:6.2":"Chattham. "}